  "prompt": "Is Roadies a reality TV show or is it scripted?",
  "response": "\"Roadies\" is primarily a reality TV show. It first premiered in India in 2003 on MTV India and has since become one of the country's most popular reality shows. The format involves contestants traveling to different locations and participating in various challenges, both physical and mental, to compete for a winning title.\n\nWhile \"Roadies\" is marketed and produced as a reality show, like many reality TV programs, there is often speculation and debate about the extent to which it is scripted or influenced by producers. Reality TV shows often involve a certain level of staging or direction to enhance entertainment value, such as guiding certain interactions or emphasizing dramatic moments. However, the core structure of \"Roadies,\" which involves real competitions and eliminations, is based on genuine contestant participation.",
